main event: Two blue-green lights were sighted traveling parallel at a high speed in the Phoenix, Arizona area.
interesting points: The objects were traveling faster than a fighter plane at an undetermined speed.
The objects traveled from around 7,700 feet to 5,500 feet altitude, covering around 10 miles in 10 seconds.
The pilot who observed the objects stated they did not conform to any known type of aircraft.
The weather conditions at the time were clear with good visibility.
No sound was detected from the objects.
witnesses: a pilot from the 127th Pilot Training Wing
